1.title: Adding two numbers
1.text: Double click on '+' to add the two numbers

1.title: Dividing two numbers
1.text: Double click on '-' to divide 1 with 2

2.title: Swapping terms in expression
2.text: Click and drag '+' to the far left side

2.title: Swapping terms in expression
2.text: Click and drag 'c' to the far left side

3.title: Swapping terms in expression
3.text: Click and drag 'b' to the far left side

3.title: Commuting & Joining
3.text: Commute the 3 to the far-left of the sum.

5.title: Commuting with fractions
5.text: Move the + into the sum to distribute

5.title: Solving fractions
5.text: Click on the fraction bar to solve it

6.title: Distributing
6.text: Move 'p' on top of '+' to factor

6.title: Distribution
6.text: Drag r on top of the other r

7.title: Commuting inside term
7.text: Move the j next to p
